---
title: Tortilla Soup with Black Beans, Corn and Bell Pepper
description: This dish is a warm and hearty vegetarian soup with a pop of crunch that will get help you through a cold winter evening! It’s veggie-packed and protein filled with a fresh avocado topping and tortillas.
